data.name: label28.Text
data.value: Defines the optimal RPM range for an automatic transmission. If outside this range, the transmission will shift to a lower / higher gear. Set values to zero to exclude this data from the engine sii file.

data.name: label27.Text
data.value: Transmission shifting range will get adjusted by these amounts based on throttle input. The more throttle is given to the truck, the more the optimal shifting range is adjusted. Set values to zero to exclude this data from the engine sii file.
